    prompt = Bioluminescent, thin ultra bold text, pulsing energy strands woven, emitting a soft cyan/neon pink hue. The letters appear alive, with slow, organic movement like flowing liquid light.  
  Nano-F
    prompt = Nano-Fractal Dust texture in a big and clear bolded typography  Text dissolves into microscopic geometric patterns hexagons, tetrahedrons that reassemble when touched. Matte metallic finish with holographic refraction.   Gravity-Defying Ink texture in a big and clear bolded typography  Letters float mid-air, warping spacetime around them. Some fragments invert into anti-matter shadows, creating a 3D illusion of depth.  
