    prompt = She is wearing whimsical heart-shaped glasses in playful colors, evoking carefree fun and youthfulness.
  Glasses Horn-rimmed
    prompt = She is wearing bold horn-rimmed glasses with thick, dark frames, channeling vintage academia and artistic spirit.
